                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="14454538" author="krosenvold" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2010 02:33:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Do you have a publicly available test project that&apos;s supposed to work with this ?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454491" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2010 03:42:49 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/exec/trunk&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://svn.apache.org/repos/asf/commons/proper/exec/trunk&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454520" author="krosenvold" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2010 07:21:30 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It seems like plexus-utils 1.5.6 is the last version to retain 1.3 compatibility. Rebuilding surefire with this version gives me a different type of problem, which may be related to my local environment not satisfying some other criteria for building the commons-proper project.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454603" author="sebb@apache.org" created="Tue, 15 Jun 2010 11:47:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just create a trivial Maven project and add a single test case.&lt;br/&gt;
Edit the surefire config &amp;lt;jvm&amp;gt; to use a 1.3 JVM instead of whatever you are using to run Maven itself.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;BTW, Surefire 2.2 seems to be the last one that works with Java 1.3.&lt;br/&gt;
Note that you must also use JUnit 3.8.1 as 3.8.2 has an assertion that requires 1.4&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454554" author="stephenc" created="Thu, 5 Aug 2010 07:04:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;r982558&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14454692" author="krosenvold" created="Mon, 29 Nov 2010 04:53:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just for the general heck of it I have restored jdk 1.3 compatibility in the upcoming surefire 2.7, and I am able to run the project you supplied with 1.3. &lt;/p&gt;


</comment>
                            <comment id="14454596" author="krosenvold" created="Tue, 14 Dec 2010 15:18:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The requirement for the PLUGIN is still 1.4 though, but forking with 1.3 now works again, so the documentation update is correct.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17993965" author="olamy" created="Fri, 4 Jul 2025 07:12:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This project has moved from Jira to GitHub Issues. This issue was migrated to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/maven-surefire/issues/1956&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;apache/maven-surefire#1956&lt;/a&gt;. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
